Dialogue: 100,0:00:04.94,0:00:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Au trecut două luni de când am ajuns în regiunea Yagumo.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:07.90,0:00:11.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Încă nu am găsit niciun indiciu despre părinții mei, dar...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:11.95,0:00:14.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Toată lumea de aici are părul negru.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:17.36,0:00:18.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cine este acela?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:22.19,0:00:23.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bună.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:24.33,0:00:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sunt un călător și caut pe cineva.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:27.38,0:00:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mi-ar plăcea foarte mult să-l pot întâlni pe primarul acestui sat.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:30.31,0:00:31.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aveți idee cine este?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:31.77,0:00:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, b-bună.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:33.54,0:00:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ești un călător? Bunica mea \Neste primarul acestui sat!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:37.30,0:00:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Serios? Dacă nu este nicio problemă, m-ai putea conduce la ea?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:41.27,0:00:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sigur.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:44.03,0:00:46.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sayo, ce tot faci? \NTe voi lăsa în urmă.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:46.83,0:00:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Așteaptă, Ruri!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:22.40,0:02:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bunico!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:25.21,0:02:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai un vizitator!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:26.88,0:02:29.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Un vizitator îmbrăcat \Ndestul de neobișnuit, văd.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:30.28,0:02:33.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Este o plăcere să vă întâlnesc. \NNumele meu este Rio.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:33.90,0:02:36.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doamnă primar, am venit aici sperând să găsesc răspunsul la câteva întrebări.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:36.78,0:02:39.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Serios? Observ că ești destul de politicos.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:39.29,0:02:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai venit dintr-o altă țară?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:41.05,0:02:44.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da, am călătorit prin multe țări.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:44.32,0:02:48.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Înțeleg. Eu sunt Yuba. \NCu ce treburi pe aici?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:48.44,0:02:50.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ei bine, caut pe cineva.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:51.06,0:02:54.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am venit în acest sat deoacere
Dialogue: 100,0:02:54.55,0:02:57.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,am auzit că dumneavoastră cunoașteți pe toată lumea din această zonă.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:57.44,0:03:00.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This seems like it's going to be \Nan involved conversation. Come in.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:00.56,0:03:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pe aici.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:02.03,0:03:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mulțumesc pentru primire.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:05.44,0:03:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am auzit că părinții mei au trăit aici,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:08.46,0:03:11.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,în regiunea Yagumo acum cincisprezece ani, dar...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:11.82,0:03:15.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Înțeleg. Care erau numele părinților tăi?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:15.45,0:03:17.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zen și Ayame.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:17.09,0:03:19.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Zen și Ayame?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:19.34,0:03:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ați mai auzit aceste nume?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:21.29,0:03:24.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ruri, Sayo, întoarceți-vă la treabă.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.26,0:03:26.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce? De ce?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:26.35,0:03:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu ar trebui să vă băgați nasul în trecutul altor persoane.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:30.18,0:03:32.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine. Just when it was getting interesting.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:32.35,0:03:33.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Să mergem, Sayo.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:33.65,0:03:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-Bine.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:36.74,0:03:39.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă mi-ai putea da puțin mai multe detalii...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:40.03,0:03:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Desigur. Am auzit că amândoi s-au născut în regiunea Yagumo.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:44.67,0:03:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father died before I was \Nold enough to know him.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:47.65,0:03:50.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I lived a peaceful, happy life\N with my mother, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:51.55,0:03:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mother died, too, when I was five.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:54.97,0:03:58.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coming to the Yagumo region was \Nsomething my mom and I promised to do.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:59.05,0:04:04.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you're bigger, I'll take you there.\N It's a place called Yagumo.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:04.52,0:04:06.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? You promised, okay?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:06.76,0:04:08.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I promise.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:09.63,0:04:13.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I traveled, I started to think that \Nif I could find where they lived,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:14.01,0:04:17.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to make graves for them.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:18.06,0:04:21.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The least I can do for them is hold \Na proper memorial in their homeland.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.15,0:04:23.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:23.61,0:04:26.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both of them are people I knew.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:26.57,0:04:29.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you do have the look of them.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:29.41,0:04:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forgive my rudeness, but how \Ndid you know my parents?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:32.49,0:04:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Zen's mother.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:33.97,0:04:34.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:35.33,0:04:36.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your grandmother.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:36.75,0:04:38.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father's...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming here.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.52,0:04:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the truth is, I don't \Nknow what to tell you.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.28,0:04:46.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We already have graves for both of them.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:46.64,0:04:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:49.66,0:04:53.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are Mother and Father's graves.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:53.43,0:04:54.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:55.10,0:04:57.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would it be all right if I paid my respects?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:58.10,0:04:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:01.85,0:05:05.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally made it here, Mother, Father.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:06.39,0:05:11.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both of them had to leave this country \Nin secret for certain reasons.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:12.25,0:05:14.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was no possibility that \Nthey would come home,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:14.33,0:05:16.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so those of us who knew of \Nthe true circumstances
Dialogue: 100,0:05:16.46,0:05:18.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,made graves for the two of them here.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:18.96,0:05:20.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was the reason?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:21.85,0:05:25.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I cannot \Nbe the one to tell you.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:25.66,0:05:28.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the time may come that \NI am able to talk about it.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:28.97,0:05:32.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think? Will you live here \Nin the village until that time comes?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:33.68,0:05:35.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would that be possible?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:35.03,0:05:38.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. You're my grandson, after all.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:38.84,0:05:41.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandchildren should \Nnever stand on manners.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.69,0:05:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandchild...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:44.30,0:05:48.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of my relatives have died. Right now, \Nit's only Ruri and I living together.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:49.13,0:05:52.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ruri is Zen's older brother's\N daughter. Your cousin.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:52.63,0:05:54.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's fifteen now.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:54.76,0:05:57.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's one year older than I am, then.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:57.98,0:06:01.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you that young? You seem quite mature.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:01.75,0:06:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm nothing like that.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:05.07,0:06:06.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall we head back?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:07.90,0:06:08.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Madame Yuba?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:09.79,0:06:11.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I stay here a little longer?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:11.92,0:06:15.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. But stop addressing me so formally.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:16.77,0:06:18.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mistress... Yuba.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:18.66,0:06:21.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Better. Don't stay out too late.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:22.27,0:06:25.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll keep your lineage hidden \Nfrom the others for a while.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:34.14,0:06:35.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse the intrusion!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:36.56,0:06:37.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly, Rio!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:37.87,0:06:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What took you so long? I'm starving!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:40.14,0:06:41.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Rio.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Let's eat!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:43.72,0:06:44.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:50.97,0:06:52.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:52.39,0:06:54.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Morning. You're up early, aren't you?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:54.76,0:06:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll start helping with things \Naround the village today.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.70,0:07:00.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd get breakfast \Nready before that.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:00.34,0:07:02.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm very happy to see \Nthat you're so motivated.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:04.27,0:07:06.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Morning, Grandma.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:06.11,0:07:07.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss Ruri—
Dialogue: 100,0:07:07.79,0:07:09.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:09.24,0:07:11.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Morning. You...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:11.95,0:07:14.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you forget that Rio's here?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:20.04,0:07:23.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! What am I doing?!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:25.45,0:07:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impressive. You're quite skilled.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.88,0:07:30.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll ask you to make miso soup.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:31.29,0:07:33.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like we don't \Nhave quite enough water.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:33.32,0:07:36.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. And Sayo and Shin \Nare coming today, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.47,0:07:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rio! Use the water over there.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:38.87,0:07:42.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We refill it every day with spirit arts.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:42.56,0:07:45.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So both of them can use spirit arts.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:45.58,0:07:48.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hot water would be better \Nthan plain water, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:48.07,0:07:49.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall I make some?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:49.64,0:07:50.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:53.38,0:07:54.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:54.41,0:07:58.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's amazing! Rio, you can make \Nhot water with spirit magic!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:58.01,0:07:59.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even Grandma can't do that!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:00.37,0:08:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a little trick to it. \NI can teach you, if you want.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:04.54,0:08:05.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:06.67,0:08:08.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:08.17,0:08:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:08.99,0:08:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm starving...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:11.03,0:08:12.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.42,0:08:13.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:13.89,0:08:14.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who're you?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:15.33,0:08:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rio and Shin haven't met yet, have they?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:17.56,0:08:20.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Sayo's older brother, Shin.\N This boy is Rio.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:20.64,0:08:22.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the son of a long-time \Nacquaintance of mine.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:22.82,0:08:25.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm called Rio. Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.46,0:08:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is so good!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.57,0:08:33.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's meat in this!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.20,0:08:35.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This miso soup is delicious, too!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:35.69,0:08:37.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rio made everything for us.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.95,0:08:38.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:38.62,0:08:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:39.82,0:08:43.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad you like it. \NIf you want, please have more.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:43.79,0:08:44.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want more!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:44.68,0:08:48.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Honestly, Big Brother, \Nshow a little restraint!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.13,0:08:52.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, it's only morning and I ate so much!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:52.80,0:08:56.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin, take Rio to Dola's place.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:56.32,0:08:57.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.92,0:09:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was thinking of having Rio be a hunter.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:00.85,0:09:03.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Him? A hunter?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:03.13,0:09:05.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Rio says he can hunt, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:05.92,0:09:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Dola said he wanted help, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:08.54,0:09:12.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's grueling work, you know?\N Does he have the stamina?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:12.75,0:09:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's built pretty delicately.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:15.24,0:09:16.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}When you want to make hot water,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:15.24,0:09:19.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll be fine. He's strong enough to have \Ntraveled to many countries at his age.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:16.75,0:09:19.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}you concentrate your will in \Nyour hand like this, and...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:19.18,0:09:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Really? I see.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:19.42,0:09:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he can use spirit arts.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:21.24,0:09:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even I can use something \Nlike the spirit arts.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:24.48,0:09:27.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He may be overwhelmingly stronger \Nthan someone like you.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:27.38,0:09:28.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bah.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:28.97,0:09:30.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Rio!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:30.58,0:09:32.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take you hunting!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.02,0:09:34.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Make sure you don't get in the way!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:34.09,0:09:35.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:35.39,0:09:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir Rio, I'm so sorry. My brother\N speaks rather sharply.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.00,0:09:40.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:40.07,0:09:42.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would it be all right for \Nme to leave the rest to you?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:42.89,0:09:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sure.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:47.10,0:09:49.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why is it "sir" Rio?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:49.25,0:09:49.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:49.81,0:09:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I mean, he sort of feels like a noble.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:53.56,0:09:55.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like someone too high up to be reached...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:55.82,0:09:57.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:06.25,0:10:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a lenou bird.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good job shooting it down, Rio!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:09.71,0:10:11.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your skills are impressive.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, we can't let \Nhim beat us, right, Shin?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:14.69,0:10:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it already!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:26.32,0:10:27.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blast it!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:27.75,0:10:31.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, let's head back. \NGood job, both of you.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:31.03,0:10:34.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today we'll be able to give everyone \Nin the village more meat than usual.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:34.30,0:10:37.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't manage to take \Ndown a single one, though.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:37.21,0:10:39.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was you and Rio that got \Nthese results, Huntmaster.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you sulking for?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:41.60,0:10:45.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the three of us working \Ntogether that got these results.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:45.23,0:10:46.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bah.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:47.37,0:10:48.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:48.40,0:10:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll talk to him later.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:50.81,0:10:52.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you come help starting tomorrow?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:52.93,0:10:54.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, you can count on me.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:57.48,0:11:00.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got pretty dirty out there.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:18.66,0:11:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Discharge.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:30.78,0:11:32.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this thing?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it must be you, Rio!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:35.49,0:11:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. That must have been a shock.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:37.88,0:11:39.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll clean it up now.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:39.49,0:11:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:41.47,0:11:43.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you make this with spirit arts, too?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:43.71,0:11:45.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I wanted to take a bath.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:45.35,0:11:46.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:46.64,0:11:47.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:49.20,0:11:50.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss Ruri?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:50.67,0:11:52.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You smell nice, Rio!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:52.60,0:11:53.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sayo, you come smell, too!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:53.98,0:11:56.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? No, I-I'm fine!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:56.42,0:11:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now. No need to get so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:04.39,0:12:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is that smell?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:05.90,0:12:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's soap.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:06.94,0:12:11.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Soap? You mean the stuff you wash yourself \Nand clothes and things with? That soap?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:11.68,0:12:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir Rio, you can make soap, too?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:14.75,0:12:16.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:18.73,0:12:19.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this thing?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:19.80,0:12:23.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Big Brother! Sir Rio made it \Nfor us! He says it's a bath!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:23.84,0:12:24.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bath?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:26.36,0:12:28.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There goes the outsider \Ntrying to score points.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:28.81,0:12:33.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really are rude. \NRio, pay no attention to him.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:33.53,0:12:37.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss Ruri is right. Big Brother, that was mean!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:37.14,0:12:41.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sayo, not you, too? Don't go getting \Nall silly over some weakling!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:41.30,0:12:43.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not being silly!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:43.61,0:12:45.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin! Rio isn't a weakling!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:45.95,0:12:48.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In spite of his looks, \Nhe's got a lot of muscle!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:48.86,0:12:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:49.45,0:12:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:50.16,0:12:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You... have you no shame?!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:52.45,0:12:53.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bleh.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:53.69,0:12:54.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:54.46,0:12:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sayo, we're going home. \NI came here to pick... you...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:00.79,0:13:01.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bah!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:28.83,0:13:30.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The crops turned out well again this year.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:30.57,0:13:33.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard that the tax examiner \Nwill be coming soon.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:33.52,0:13:34.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:35.22,0:13:39.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right. Given your skills,\N I have a favor to ask you.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:39.18,0:13:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:40.00,0:13:42.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the annual tribute and our own rations,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:42.54,0:13:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the rice that remains is to \Nbe sold in the royal capital.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:45.90,0:13:49.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could I ask you to guard the transport team?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:49.21,0:13:50.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you think I'm good enough.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:50.55,0:13:51.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a great help.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:52.14,0:13:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a fight!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:53.47,0:13:55.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Shin and those guys\N from the other village!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:58.82,0:14:02.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gon! Who do you think you are \Njust walking around our village?!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:03.23,0:14:06.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you're just heading into the \Nbathing hut like it's nothing!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:06.26,0:14:07.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:07.11,0:14:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:08.32,0:14:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm here as a guest to visit the head \Nof your village. That should be obvious.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:13.43,0:14:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ruri... You've grown into quite \Nthe woman since I last saw you.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And behind you is...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:19.46,0:14:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't look at my little sister \Nwith those filthy eyes!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:22.24,0:14:24.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's your sister, is she?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:24.39,0:14:26.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, she's a stunner.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:27.99,0:14:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:29.05,0:14:30.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin, don't!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:30.43,0:14:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you punch this guy over these \Npathetic taunts, it'll cause problems.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:33.58,0:14:36.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He may be rotten, but he's the son of \Nthe head of the neighboring village!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:37.58,0:14:41.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gon, why are you here in our village anyway?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:41.17,0:14:43.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me stay at your place, won't you?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:43.68,0:14:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:44.69,0:14:48.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way to sell trade\N goods in the royal capital.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:48.07,0:14:52.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but unfortunately, my cart broke. \NIt'll take time to repair.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:52.99,0:14:55.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we'll lend you one of our guest huts.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:55.64,0:15:00.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now. I might be your husband \None day. That's pretty cold of you.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:00.34,0:15:03.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Don't say weird things \Nlike that! It's disgusting!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:03.52,0:15:07.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The head of this village \Nonly has you for an heir.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:07.89,0:15:11.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I'm saying I'll volunteer \Nto be your husband.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:11.52,0:15:15.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious! \NWe villagers will never allow it!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:15.01,0:15:15.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:15.97,0:15:19.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? None of you are \NRuri's man, but you're jealous?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:19.56,0:15:21.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a bunch of sissies.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:21.63,0:15:23.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:23.41,0:15:24.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bring it on.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:24.48,0:15:25.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You piece of crap!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:25.44,0:15:26.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:31.64,0:15:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end, this is all you've got?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:34.49,0:15:35.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:35.77,0:15:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:36.99,0:15:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:38.83,0:15:41.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Old Lady Yuba. It's been a while.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:41.73,0:15:45.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, let him go! Talk comes after that.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:48.20,0:15:49.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Big Brother!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:49.34,0:15:50.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:53.94,0:15:55.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:55.39,0:15:58.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gon, I apologize for Shin and\N the others' misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:59.26,0:16:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But your behavior was imprudent, too.\N You went too far.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:04.04,0:16:07.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tonight, we will lend you a guest \Nhut at the edge of the village.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:07.81,0:16:10.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you are not allowed to \Nleave it. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:10.70,0:16:11.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:17.93,0:16:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A newcomer?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:19.12,0:16:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's effeminate. I don't like him.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:28.04,0:16:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Big Bro?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:28.72,0:16:30.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear. Are you all right?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:30.42,0:16:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:32.12,0:16:34.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's nothing. Let's go.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:34.38,0:16:36.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, now my clothes are dirty.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:38.59,0:16:41.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone just go back home \Nquietly for today, all right?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:41.18,0:16:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've forbidden them from leaving the hut,\N but don't let down your guard!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:44.78,0:16:46.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gran.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:46.50,0:16:49.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you let Sayo stay with you for a while?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:49.49,0:16:52.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two of us live alone, so...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:52.25,0:16:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think she'd feel safer \Nwith you and Ruri around.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:56.64,0:16:58.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's no problem.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:58.11,0:16:59.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sayo, that's what we'll do.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:59.55,0:17:00.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, Madame.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:06.06,0:17:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should go to sleep.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:07.67,0:17:08.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:09.21,0:17:10.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss Ruri, Miss Sayo...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:10.76,0:17:11.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir Rio...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:11.91,0:17:14.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please put this in a corner of your room.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:14.78,0:17:16.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a protective amulet.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:16.44,0:17:17.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A protective amulet?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:17.34,0:17:18.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:18.36,0:17:20.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir Rio, thank you so much!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:22.69,0:17:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's our big bro for you!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:25.15,0:17:29.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course. I made sure to \Nbust up the cart really well.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:31.55,0:17:34.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can take all day tomorrow \Nrepairing it at our leisure.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:35.11,0:17:37.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fun comes after that.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:40.85,0:17:41.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Madame Yuba!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:43.01,0:17:44.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:44.47,0:17:46.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome! Thank you for coming all this way!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:46.67,0:17:48.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you. I'm called Rio.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:49.17,0:17:51.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm called Saga Hayate.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:51.51,0:17:54.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm traveling to all the \Nvillages as tax examiner.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:54.62,0:17:56.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll take good \Ncare of my aides, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:22.39,0:18:24.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watching like that can't possibly be any fun.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:25.98,0:18:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your movement's so pretty, \Nwe couldn't help watching!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:28.75,0:18:30.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just simple training.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:30.45,0:18:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, it's really impressive!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:32.49,0:18:34.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've done it every day since \Nyou came to the village, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:34.81,0:18:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you start martial arts?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:37.03,0:18:38.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:39.00,0:18:41.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if I die, I'll protect you, Mii-chan!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:42.58,0:18:45.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a little embarrassing to say...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:45.40,0:18:47.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? I want to know even \Nmore now! Right, Sayo?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:47.95,0:18:50.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Yes. I'd like to know.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:50.68,0:18:53.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, this is a problem.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:53.24,0:18:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you mind if I dress myself?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:55.31,0:18:57.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, please go ahead.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:58.38,0:19:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was little, \Nthere was a girl I liked...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:01.04,0:19:04.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to become strong enough \Nthat I could protect her.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:04.34,0:19:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, really?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:06.19,0:19:08.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is she doing now?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:08.57,0:19:10.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're not in contact anymore.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:10.41,0:19:12.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She might be with someone she loves.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:13.35,0:19:16.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I don't know if she even \Nremembers me in the first place.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:20.33,0:19:22.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know where she's living, either.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:23.13,0:19:26.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if she's alive, then you \Nmight meet again one day.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:26.90,0:19:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Sayo?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:28.42,0:19:29.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:29.73,0:19:31.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:31.05,0:19:33.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though, right now, I'm training for myself.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:34.23,0:19:36.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That bath was truly wonderful!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:37.13,0:19:38.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:38.53,0:19:39.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:40.71,0:19:44.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss Ruri, you two should go ahead and \Nuse the bath first. It's getting chilly.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:44.37,0:19:45.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:45.77,0:19:47.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go then, Sayo.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:47.28,0:19:48.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:11.58,0:20:13.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quiet. I'm not responsible for \Nwhat happens if you struggle.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:15.61,0:20:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss Ruri!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:18.63,0:20:21.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you make a fuss, I'll punch\N her right in the face.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:21.22,0:20:22.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:22.94,0:20:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:25.46,0:20:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 100,0:20:36.55,0:20:37.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:38.29,0:20:39.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crap.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:53.17,0:20:56.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,St...op...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:57.72,0:20:59.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:13.74,0:21:14.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir Rio...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:15.98,0:21:17.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir Rio, stop!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:19.17,0:21:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:21.92,0:21:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir Rio! Cease! If you hit \Nhim any more, he'll die!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:34.56,0:21:36.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that Gon?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:36.59,0:21:40.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems he was trying to assault \NLady Ruri and Lady Sayo.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:40.31,0:21:41.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll handle this.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:41.87,0:21:43.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lady Yuba, please see to the two of them.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:43.42,0:21:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ruri, Sayo, come with me.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:48.90,0:21:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I correct in that you lot are \Nthe ones who caused this uproar?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:52.08,0:21:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y...es...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:54.10,0:21:56.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have committed a grave crime.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:56.59,0:21:59.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I seek punishment from the kingdom.\N Send a messenger!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:59.46,0:22:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:05.59,0:22:08.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the second time I've \Nwanted to kill someone.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:10.22,0:22:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As Rio, I've had this feeling \Ninside me all this time.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:14.61,0:22:15.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 100,0:22:16.56,0:22:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}without me noticing,
Dialogue: 100,0:22:18.58,0:22:20.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been pulled closer to Amakawa Haruto.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:22.75,0:22:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I turned my eyes away from my revenge.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:26.01,0:22:27.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though, in the end, I...
Dialogue: 100,0:22:28.84,0:22:32.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the same sort of person as that man.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:39.23,0:22:41.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow morning, a messenger \Nfrom the kingdom will arrive.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:41.66,0:22:44.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They've decided that Gon and the \Nothers will be taken into custody.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:45.50,0:22:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:47.28,0:22:51.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I caused you such trouble yesterday. \NI can't apologize enough.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:51.89,0:22:56.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to apologize for. \NThank you for protecting Ruri and Sayo.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:57.13,0:23:01.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's only because you arrived \Nso quickly that I was safe.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:01.39,0:23:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir Rio, it was only because you wanted \Nto protect us that you got so angry!
Dialogue: 100,0:23:06.43,0:23:10.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't hit him, Sir Rio, I would have.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:11.29,0:23:14.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone... thank you so much.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:14.16,0:23:17.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, please... let me apologize \Njust one more time.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:17.89,0:23:19.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so serious.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:20.01,0:23:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like a certain someone.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:22.69,0:23:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 100,0:23:23.74,0:23:25.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's have breakfast.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:25.74,0:23:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir Rio, I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 100,0:23:27.93,0:23:30.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Let's hurry and eat!
Dialogue: 100,0:23:36.95,0:23:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"Descendența regală."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:07.90,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,Toamna anului 998 al Erei Sfinte
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:25.06,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,Țara promisă
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:39.98,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,Data viitoare
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:39.98,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,Descendența regală
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:49.99,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,By Minazuki Futago
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.98,0:23:42.48,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,Rio! Haide să luăm prânzul împreună!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.48,0:23:44.48,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,Bine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:46.98,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,Rio! Haide să facem baie împreună!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.98,0:23:49.99,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,Bine...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.63,0:23:50.25,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,Ce?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.63,0:23:50.25,DedzuyaSigns,,0,0,0,,Hi-hi
